  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3968340/extras/3077d2a79104f34e543289b823e5ad56.webp?t=1774107135\" width=524 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The aliens have arrived...and <strong>YOU</strong> are in the cockpit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take flight through the foggy spot-lit skies of 1950s B-movie Americana in this interstellar arcade action romp! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blast your laser to lure the gullible humans out of their hiding places and then pull them up into your ship. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach the quota to move on to the next level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3968340/extras/a53ff78400f858bdea4843ed1fdf2c2f.poster.avif?t=1774107135\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3968340/extras/a53ff78400f858bdea4843ed1fdf2c2f.webm?t=1774107135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3968340/extras/a53ff78400f858bdea4843ed1fdf2c2f.mp4?t=1774107135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3968340/extras/5fa0a0e111495c3c7c32e292da553dd8.webp?t=1774107135\" width=571 height=52 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assault humanity alone or partner up with a fellow invader. Co-operate  or  compete to capture the most filthy bipeds in a single session (don't forget about the cows)!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The power to destroy is in your hands now...those <strong>FOOLISH EARTHLINGS</strong> won't know what hit them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3968340/extras/3a9bee35551775ac6b44823208e8c8c8.webp?t=1774107135\" width=418 height=52 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local multiplayer on PC requires at least 1 controller.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3968340/extras/3077d2a79104f34e543289b823e5ad56.webp?t=1774107135\" width=524 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The aliens have arrived...and <strong>YOU</strong> are in the cockpit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take flight through the foggy spot-lit skies of 1950s B-movie Americana in this interstellar arcade action romp! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blast your laser to lure the gullible humans out of their hiding places and then pull them up into your ship. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach the quota to move on to the next level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3968340/extras/a53ff78400f858bdea4843ed1fdf2c2f.poster.avif?t=1774107135\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3968340/extras/a53ff78400f858bdea4843ed1fdf2c2f.webm?t=1774107135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3968340/extras/a53ff78400f858bdea4843ed1fdf2c2f.mp4?t=1774107135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3968340/extras/5fa0a0e111495c3c7c32e292da553dd8.webp?t=1774107135\" width=571 height=52 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assault humanity alone or partner up with a fellow invader. Co-operate  or  compete to capture the most filthy bipeds in a single session (don't forget about the cows)!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The power to destroy is in your hands now...those <strong>FOOLISH EARTHLINGS</strong> won't know what hit them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3968340/extras/3a9bee35551775ac6b44823208e8c8c8.webp?t=1774107135\" width=418 height=52 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local multiplayer on PC requires at least 1 controller.</p>",
